# Refurb Genius Project Rules

Refurb Genius is the first app in a future 3-product property intelligence platform.

Future products:
- Refurb Genius: consumer/investor refurbishment analysis app
- Deal Copilot: property acquisition automation app
- Refurb IQ: QS/design/construction professional app

Current priority:
Build and harden Refurb Genius first.

Architecture rule:
Keep shared business logic reusable for all future apps.

Shared core must live in:
- src/core/types
- src/core/constants
- src/core/projects
- src/core/pricing
- src/core/roi
- src/core/reports
- src/core/ai

Do not duplicate business logic inside pages/components.

AI rule:
AI may assist with summaries, condition analysis, recommendations, and visual concepts.
AI must not generate pricing, ROI, VAT, profit, or financial calculations.

Pricing and ROI must be deterministic.
